{
  "rewrites": [
    { "source": "/api/(.*)", "destination": "/api/$1" }
  ],
  "functions": {
    "api/anthropic.js": {
      "memory": 1024,
      "maxDuration": 30
    }
  }
}
```

This tells Vercel:
- Serve `index.html` as the main page
- Route `/api/*` requests to the API functions

Then your API will be available at:
```
https://boba-scanner.vercel.app/api/anthropic
```

